794
01:13:14,570 --> 01:13:16,650
Sudah terlambat untuk itu.

795
01:13:46,430 --> 01:13:47,850
Jacob!

796
01:13:49,850 --> 01:13:51,640
Di bawah sini! Dia di sini!

